WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:55.220 --> 00:01:05.739
Try to use the best quality chocolate you can find 
 as it will matter in the taste.  

00:01:08.419 --> 00:01:15.552
Using a kitchen knife, finely chop the chocolate 
 and place it in a bowl. 

00:01:21.994 --> 00:01:24.543
Heat the heavy cream until it becomes hot 
 but should not reach a boiling point.

00:01:38.322 --> 00:01:49.650
Pour the heavy cream over the chopped chocolate and 
 let it sit for 1 minute. 

00:01:51.410 --> 00:01:59.460
Then using a spatula stir the chocolate until completely melted. 

00:02:19.757 --> 00:02:35.270
Pour the chocolate cream on top of the Nutella (in 
 a separate bowl) and mix them until completely incorporated.

00:02:40.501 --> 00:02:45.800
Cover the bowl and place in the fridge for at 
 least one hour until it becomes solid. 

00:03:00.146 --> 00:03:05.320
Once the truffle mixture gets cold, take it out from 
 the fridge and roll it into small balls.

00:03:08.499 --> 00:03:17.330
Roll the bolls in coconut, chopped nuts, cocoa powder, 
 etc. or anyting coating for your choice.

00:04:07.816 --> 00:04:20.610
Place the truffles in a plate then in the fridge 
 for at least 1 hour before serving. Bon Appetit!

